  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Patients participating in this observational study previously participated in one of the
        phase I-II studies for the compound
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Patient randomized, treated and alive at the end of the phase I-II study
             participation, irrespective of their treatment group,

          -  Who signed the TALISMAN survey informed consent (or for deceased patients, the
             informed consent was signed the legal representative/family member as per national
             regulations - except in countries where Ethics Committee approval only is required for
             retrospective data collection).

        The above information is not intended to contain all considerations relevant to a patient's
        potential participation in a clinical trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
